:10<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，留意到有網民號召明日早上，在香港各區堵塞不同的主要運輸幹道，目的為癱瘓交通、拖延警力，以配合圍堵立法會之違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n警方嚴厲譴責煽動他人擾亂公共秩序的行為，指非法堵路不單危害道路安全及影響道路使用者，更會阻礙緊急救援的服務，嚴重者更可引致他人生命受到威脅。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，絕不容忍任何破壞社會安寧的違法行為，定會果斷執法，包括拘捕違法者及迅速拖走造成嚴重阻塞的車輛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528482-20200526.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528482-20200526.htm&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMAwsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=419287ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528482-20200526.htm&h=4167a812\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528482-20200526.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>放心，警方會確保你一定返到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3f7b3d0cccee7124cc0ee366dac9653ba7baf488","tid":2036524,"uid":197716,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:02:38.000Z","msg":"見到想返工既<br />\n我見一個打一個"},{"pid":"974d9b4795dee765d6f98309cb018a6bce94d94c","tid":2036524,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f7b3d0cccee7124cc0ee366dac9653ba7baf488","tid":2036524,"uid":197716,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:02:38.000Z","msg":"見到想返工既<br />\n我見一個打一個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:01:53.000Z","msg":"體諒下，要交租又要養家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17334140ab9bccb688fcd86cff169e183652730","tid":2036524,"uid":117792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"974d9b4795dee765d6f98309cb018a6bce94d94c","tid":2036524,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f7b3d0cccee7124cc0ee366dac9653ba7baf488","tid":2036524,"uid":197716,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:02:38.000Z","msg":"見到想返工既<br />\n我見一個打一個"},"cited